{"title":"厦门歌","authors":["里局"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":11,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里局"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门岛，厦门岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上浪万丈高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白鹭衔来花籽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里种下花草。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门岛，厦门岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨石当作鼓敲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石柱好像是森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它要挡住美国佬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门岛，厦门岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红荔枝，绿香蕉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸老虎干瞪眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它想吃它吃不到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门岛，厦门岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海里筑长堤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倘使鲁班还活着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一定要来请教。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门岛，祝你好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是祖国的光荣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面向滔滔大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹起英雄号角。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方巨人命令我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来和厦门结知交，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着万炮齐鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着万顷浪涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸老虎伸起脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑乌鸦也在怪叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是多么可恶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要高呼开炮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮我请你怒吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮我请你呼号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万支火箭齐发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨上大海奔跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门岛，祝你好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群星在空中高照，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千只帆船出港，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船帆有如飞鸟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群鸟呵，飞行吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗在海上飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼雷为你送行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大炮为你开道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄城，英雄岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住着无数英豪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一座海上半岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本是英雄的城堡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岛上炉火在燃烧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢花海涛相照耀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹奏吧英雄号角，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点放吧祖国巨炮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门岛，英雄岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在祖国最前哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇士点起和平灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的灯高高照。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们来到英雄岛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你感到骄傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你歌，为你唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你舞，为你欢笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们走上阵地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拜战士做老师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把大炮当做笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把海水当做墨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里纵情高歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪管词句好不好；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愿做一头白鹭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种下几棵花草；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愿做一颗炮弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓死那美国佬！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}